wv
  • Reference

Summary Maximum Overlap Discrete Wavelet Transform

Unlists MODWT object and places it in matrix form

# S3 method for modwt
summary(object, ...)

Arguments

object

A modwt object
...

additional arguments affecting the summary produced.

Value

Prints the modwt matrix decomposition

Examples

set.seed(999)
x = rnorm(100)
summary(modwt(x))
